---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import scrollpic2 from "../assets/images/awkward2.png";
---

<section class="text-pillowtalk-500 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 py-16 px-16">
  <div class="max-w-xl text-pretty">
    <h2 class="font-montserrat text-heading2 font-extrabold tracking-tighter pb-12">not another solo dating app.</h2>
    <p class="pb-6">we started Doubble, because we believe you're the best version of yourself, when you're with your friends.</p>
    <p class="pb-6">the group chat flows more easily, when you're four people. it feels more comfortable having your friend with you. aaand it's just more fun.</p>
    <p>enough talking. go try it out yourself 🍀</p>
  </div>
  <div><Image src={scrollpic2} alt="pizza party" class="rounded-3xl" /></div>
</section>
